{"tid":2424158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登上任後首次動武！下令空襲敘利亞親伊朗民兵組織","createTime":"2021-02-26T10:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T11:04:47.000Z","uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e42bf28a2d8c0359568adebe0a8b65cdbf1dec7","tid":2424158,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wealth.com.tw/home/articles/30252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wealth.com.tw%2Fhome%2Farticles%2F30252&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=f962b826\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wealth.com.tw/home/articles/30252</a><br />\n美國總統拜登(Joe Biden)當地時間25日，指示五角大廈空襲位於敍利亞東部、親伊朗民兵組織的據點，為拜登上任後首次軍事行動。資料照。（圖／NOWnews）<br />\n波斯灣局勢再度亮警報，美國總統拜登(Joe Biden)當地時間25日，指示五角大廈空襲位於敍利亞東部、親伊朗民兵組織的據點，為拜登上任後的首次軍事行動。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，本月中旬，美軍駐伊拉克北部基地附近的埃爾比勒國際機場外區域，遭到數枚火箭襲擊，造成至少1死8傷，包括美國軍人，22日又傳出有至少2枚火箭彈落在巴格達綠區（Green Zone）範圍內，為美國及其他外國使館所在地。<br />\n美國國防部發言人科比(John Kirby)聲稱，這次的行動獲拜登批准，是對敵方發起的等比例軍事回應，同時配合外交措施，強調「總統一定會採取行動保護美國和聯軍人員。」"},{"pid":"10f5db8e0d95359a251e7a8c6b4f31e4babcbfc1","tid":2424158,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"The world is watching"},{"pid":"4d8b0ab3f88f5e8404efa8e1f3b052cef74bc9ab","tid":2424158,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"牙joe ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f705acbe2d49fea8775c71aa0e9fdf983d37da81","tid":2424158,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"軍火商，CIA又可以揾食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d848377ac34b5d32977736a114072ef030aa403c","tid":2424158,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"炸緬甸啦屌<br />\n炸9哂D 黑軍"}]}